data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!!!SELLER MOTIVATED! Welcome to this exquisite 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, where elegance meets comfort. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of laminate flooring throughout the entire downstairs, complemented by numerous upgraded finishes. The kitchen is a chef's dream with white 42-inch cabinets, a tasteful tile backsplash, and gorgeous granite countertops.  The master bedroom, conveniently located downstairs, offers a peaceful retreat with an oversized walk in shower. Two additional bedrooms are also thoughtfully placed on the first floor, providing ease and versatility.  Upstairs, you'll discover a large bonus room, perfect for various activities, and a spacious private bedroom with a full bathroom that adds convenience and privacy.  Outside, the home is surrounded by beautiful landscaping, and a covered lanai offers the perfect spot for outdoor relaxation, making this house a true haven of comfort and style.
